b> and roll in breadcrumbs. Cook for <b>10-15 minutes<b> (180°C), turning during cooking, until golden brown. Two meals in one!","The consistency of the soup can be altered according to your preference. If you want a more soupy soup, add <b>50-100 g<b> more water in <b>step 4.<b>"],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","35m","6 portions"]}